the second type of style sheet is 
Internal
ex:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<title>Internal CSS</title>
		<style>
			.main {
				text-align:center;
			}
			.GFG {
				color:#009900;
				font-size:50px;
				font-weight:bold;
			}
			.geeks {
				font-style:bold;
				font-size:20px;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class = "main">
			<div class ="GFG">Mafia</div>
			
			<div class ="geeks">
				A world below darkness
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>			
